description: Residential redevelopment involving the erection of buildings ranging from four to 6 storeys for 82 residential units (22x1 bed, 32x2 bed, 20x3 bed and 8x4 bed) with basement car parking for 42 vehicles with vehicle access via Papermill Place (Phase 1 and 2, 24 Sutherland Road) off St Andrews Road & Stirling Road, cycle parking (138 spaces - total surface and within basement), motorcycle parking (9 spaces), refuse and recycling storage facilities, inclusion of land for the provision of a public open space fronting Sutherland Road proposals amending Planning Statement, Design, Access and sustainability Statement and Parking Management Strategy, Transport Statement, Air Quality Assessment and Renewable Energy Strategy approved in principle on 06/01/09. (Revised proposals)
